Description: SecuBox Console TUI — Terminal Dashboard
 Terminal-based dashboard for SecuBox appliances using Python Textual.
 Provides system monitoring, service management, and network status
 via a TUI that auto-starts on TTY1 when GUI kiosk is disabled.
 .
 Features:
  - Live system metrics (CPU, memory, disk)
  - Service management with start/stop/restart
  - Network interface status with WAN/LAN classification
  - Real-time log viewer with filtering
  - Vim-style keyboard navigation
  - Board-specific theming (MOCHAbin, ESPRESSObin, etc.)
 .
 Port Debian bookworm de SecuBox-DEB (CyberMind.fr).
